      • main

        public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
        Starts a capsule system with the default execution profile. The 0th arg is interpreted to be the root capsule from which the system will be started.
        Parameters:
        args - The root capsule's name followed by the arguments to be passed into the root capsule's `main()` method.

      • start

        public static void start(java.lang.Class<? extends org.paninij.runtime.Panini$Capsule$Root> root,
                         java.lang.String[] args)
        Starts a capsule system from the given root capsule using the default execution profile.
        Parameters:
        root - The class of the capsule which will act as the root capsule.
        args - The arguments to be passed into the root capsule's `main()` method.

      • start

        public static void start(java.lang.Class<? extends org.paninij.runtime.Panini$Capsule$Root> root,
                         ExecutionProfile profile,
                         java.lang.String[] args)
        Starts a capsule system from the given root capsule using the given execution profile.
        Parameters:
        root - The class of the capsule which will act as the root capsule.
        profile - The execution profile with which the capsule system will run.
        args - The arguments to be passed into the root capsule's `main()` method.
